    <title><![CDATA[PHP 获取 文件大小,类型,创建/修改时间]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.wabzsy.com/2012/08/22/PHP-%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F-%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA-%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/"/>
    <id>http://blog.wabzsy.com/2012/08/22/PHP-获取-文件大小-类型-创建-修改时间/</id>
    <published>2012-08-22T15:00:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-10-06T19:28:08.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>常用函数:</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">int filesize(string <span class="variable">$filename</span>);<span class="comment">//取得文件大小</span></div><div class="line">string filetype(string <span class="variable">$filename</span>);<span class="comment">//取得文件类型</span></div><div class="line">int filemtime(string <span class="variable">$filename</span>);<span class="comment">//取得文件修改时间</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>获取文件大小:</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">&lt;?php</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="variable">$filename</span> = <span class="string">'test.txt'</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$filename</span>.<span class="string">'文件大小为: '</span>.filesize(<span class="variable">$filename</span>).<span class="string">' bytes'</span>;</div><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">?&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>获取文件类型:</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">&lt;?php</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="variable">$filename</span> = <span class="string">'test.txt'</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> filetype(<span class="variable">$filename</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">?&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p> <strong>filetype</strong> 有八种返回结果:</p>
<p><strong>fifo</strong>,<strong>char</strong>,<strong>dir</strong>,<strong>block</strong>,<strong>link</strong>,<strong>file</strong>,<strong>unknown</strong>和<strong>false</strong></p>
<p>常见返回结果主要是<strong>file</strong>和<strong>dir</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>获取文件修改时间:</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">&lt;?php</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="variable">$filename</span> = <span class="string">"test.txt"</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"$filename 修改日期为："</span>,date(<span class="string">"Y-m-d H:i:s"</span>,filemtime(<span class="variable">$filename</span>));</div><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">?&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>filemtime()</strong>返回值为<strong><em>UNIX</em></strong>格式的时间戳,要用<strong>date()</strong>函数来格式化</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
